parameters:
When I think about that day, I can't fall asleep and wake
up.
Today, I'm more lost in thought than usual.

Is it because I graduated without understanding
anything...?

Before I knew it, I found myself heading towards that <N
village>.

\N<Sayama> It seems like today was the graduation
ceremony...

<Hinata Aki> It doesn't matter since I left home and quit
school.

<Hinata Aki> Geez... Saying something like that now,
Sayama-san, you're so mean...

\N<Sayama> If you're going to be so intense... I can't take
it anymore...

\N<Hinata Aki> Ahaha... Sayama-san, you're ejaculating too
much... Lately, you've been ejaculating a lot, haven't you?
<K♥>

\N<Sayama> Hehe... Lately, I've been feeling more
energetic.

\N<Hinata Aki> Indeed, Sayama-san has been working hard
lately, hasn't he?

\N<Sayama> Hehe... Actually, I've been working hard and
saving money to buy this...
\N<Hinata Aki> Hey... why did you buy something like this!

\N<Sayama> I wanted to do it while wearing it on graduation
day... hehe

\N<Hinata Aki> Ugh... even though you don't have any money,
you're wasting it... idiot
\N<Sayama> Really! Are you sure it's okay?

<Hinata Aki> You're getting too excited... And also...
Don't be too rough, okay?
